<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>战区</title><link>https://www.twz.com</link><description>防御世界的强大进攻。</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 17 May 2026 03:26:14 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>带有巨大车顶的神秘中国SUV出现在北京特朗普车队中</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/mysterious-chinese-suv-with-massive-roof-featured-in-trump-motorcade-in-beijing</link><description>&lt;p&gt;这些看起来怪异的高顶SUV是特朗普总统最近访问中国期间在其车队中发现的几辆著名车辆之一。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/mysterious-chinese-suv-with-massive-roof-featured-in-trump-motorcade-in-beijing"&gt;特朗普北京车队中的这款带有巨大车顶的神秘中国SUV&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;中。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 May 2026 22:54:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/mysterious-chinese-suv-with-massive-roof-featured-in-trump-motorcade-in-beijing</guid></item><item><title>地堡谈话：让我们谈谈本周我们做过和没有涵盖的所有事情</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/bunker-talk-lets-talk-about-all-the-things-we-did-and-didnt-cover-this-week-192</link><description>&lt;p&gt;水有金属味。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/bunker-talk-lets-talk-about-all-the-things-we-did-and-didnt-cover-this-week-192"&gt;《地堡谈话：让我们谈谈本周我们做过和没有涵盖的所有事情》&lt;/a&gt;一文首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 May 2026 22:13:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/bunker-talk-lets-talk-about-all-the-things-we-did-and-didnt-cover-this-week-192</guid></item><item><title>阿根廷退役 A-4 战鹰</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/argentina-retires-its-a-4-fightinghawks</link><description>&lt;p&gt;经过六十年的服役，A-4 的第一家出口运营商终于放弃了天鹰战斗机，推出了第一架 F-16。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/argentina-retires-its-a-4-fightinghawks"&gt;阿根廷 A-4 战鹰退役后&lt;/a&gt;的报道首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 May 2026 19:20:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/argentina-retires-its-a-4-fightinghawks</guid></item><item><title>神秘的 AIM-260 空对空导弹终于突破掩护</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/secretive-aim-260-air-to-air-missile-finally-breaks-cover</link><description>&lt;p&gt;AIM-260 已经开发多年，是备受推崇的 AIM-120 AMRAAM 急需的远程后继产品。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/secretive-aim-260-air-to-air-missile-finally-breaks-cover"&gt;秘密 AIM-260 空对空导弹终于突破掩护&lt;/a&gt;后首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 May 2026 17:39:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/secretive-aim-260-air-to-air-missile-finally-breaks-cover</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰拦截无人机创新技术击落数千架俄罗斯沙赫德</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/inside-ukraines-interceptor-drone-innovations-swatting-down-thousands-of-shahed-drones</link><description>&lt;p&gt;Brave1 首席执行官 Andrii Hrytseniuk 为我们提供了有关乌克兰以低廉成本对抗俄罗斯单向攻击无人机舰队的能力的独家见解。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/inside-ukraines-interceptor-drone-innovations-swatting-down-thousands-of-shahed-drones"&gt;乌克兰拦截无人机创新内部击落数千名俄罗斯沙赫德的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;“战区”&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 May 2026 17:29:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/inside-ukraines-interceptor-drone-innovations-swatting-down-thousands-of-shahed-drones</guid></item><item><title>中央司令部指挥官驳斥了有关伊朗保留大部分导弹和无人机武器库的报道（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/centcom-commander-dismisses-reports-that-iran-retains-most-of-its-missile-and-drone-arsenal</link><description>&lt;p&gt;海军上将布拉德·库珀表示，“我在开源中看到的数字并不准确”，因为有报道称伊朗的大部分武库完好无损。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/centcom-commander-dismisses-reports-that-iran-retains-most-of-its-missile-and-drone-arsenal"&gt;中央司令部指挥官否认伊朗保留其大部分导弹和无人机武器库的报道（更新）&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 May 2026 00:39:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/centcom-commander-dismisses-reports-that-iran-retains-most-of-its-missile-and-drone-arsenal</guid></item><item><title>核动力特朗普级战列舰将扭转海军“最大的错误”之一：海军老板</title><link>https://www.twz.com/sea/nuclear-powered-trump-class-battleships-will-reverse-one-of-the-navys-largest-mistakes-navy-boss</link><description>&lt;p&gt;海军作战部长表示，放弃核动力水面舰艇是他服役以来做出的最糟糕的决定之一。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;后&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/sea/nuclear-powered-trump-class-battleships-will-reverse-one-of-the-navys-largest-mistakes-navy-boss"&gt;核动力特朗普级战列舰将扭转海军“最大的错误”之一：海军老大&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 May 2026 20:08:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/sea/nuclear-powered-trump-class-battleships-will-reverse-one-of-the-navys-largest-mistakes-navy-boss</guid></item><item><title>以色列 F-35 正在配备外部油箱</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/israels-f-35s-are-getting-external-fuel-tanks</link><description>&lt;p&gt;刚刚结束针对伊朗的大规模作战行动后，以色列正在通过外部油箱提高 F-35I 阿迪尔的续航能力，这也将减少对加油机的依赖。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/israels-f-35s-are-getting-external-fuel-tanks"&gt;以色列 F-35 正在配备外部油箱的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 May 2026 17:45:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/israels-f-35s-are-getting-external-fuel-tanks</guid></item><item><title>MQ-9 Reaper 的更换要求给无人机带来了压力，价格足够便宜，以至于有丢失的风险</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/mq-9-reaper-replacement-requirements-stress-a-drone-cheap-enough-to-risk-losing</link><description>&lt;p&gt;空军的 MQ-9“死神”后继机将以生存能力换取更低的成本、更广泛的任务和大规模生产。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/mq-9-reaper-replacement-requirements-stress-a-drone-cheap-enough-to-risk-losing"&gt;MQ-9 Reaper 后更换要求强调一架便宜到足以冒丢失风险的无人机&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 May 2026 21:55:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/mq-9-reaper-replacement-requirements-stress-a-drone-cheap-enough-to-risk-losing</guid></item><item><title>五角大楼制定三年采购1万枚低成本巡航导弹的计划（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/sea/10000-low-cost-cruise-missiles-in-three-years-procurement-plan-laid-out-by-pentagon</link><description>&lt;p&gt;美国军方现在还计划购买 12,000 枚“廉价”高超音速导弹，作为加强弹药库存的更大努力的一部分。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/sea/10000-low-cost-cruise-missiles-in-three-years-procurement-plan-laid-out-by-pentagon"&gt;五角大楼制定的三年内采购10,000枚低成本巡航导弹的计划（更新）&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 May 2026 20:10:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/sea/10000-low-cost-cruise-missiles-in-three-years-procurement-plan-laid-out-by-pentagon</guid></item></channel></rss>